y camera have a fake power cable these features make the dummy cameras almost exact replicas of the real cameras dummy cameras are a low cost solution if youre not able to spend the money on a real  surveillance camera a dummy camera can also be a cheap way to add on to an existing surveillance system although dummy cameras wont catch a criminal studies have shown that just the presence of a fake camera has prevented crimes like robbery theft and vandalism   read more      cart is empty total    cart is empty  select taser models  the affordable and preferred nonlethal choice of most law enforcement agencies private security and regular citizens gunlike nonlethal weapons like the taser devices are often seen on television or in the news where an officer has to subdue a person who is not complying with his verbal commands to stop and desist the subject is often seen posing a threat to him or herself or others and has to be incapacitated for the safety of the officers or of others in the vicinity taser handheld weapons have been shown to be extremely effective in taking down even the most aggressive person   each advanced taser® gun model uses a replaceable cartridge unit which employs compressed nitrogen to fire two barbed probes at  feet per second these probes are connected to the weapon by highvoltage insulated wire when the probes make contact with the target the advanced air taser handgun transmits powerful electrical pulses along the wires and into the body of the target through up to two inches of clothing                                               police stun guns     taser cartridges  batteries   taser gun holsters   taser® advanced taser® and taser pulse are registered trademarks of taser international inc         click her for the taser xp          click here for the taser cbolt           click here for the new taser pulse       click here for the new taser x defender   new  taser strike light         order yours today              click here for the ne