m safety for both the user and the assailant by bringing dangerous situations quickly under control before force escalates to lethal levels there have been hundreds of reports that taser devices disabled attackers and probably saved the owners life how can the taser device be so effective yet noninjurious the taser device does not depend upon impact pain or body penetration to achieve its effect its pulsating electrical output interferes with communication between the brain and the muscular system resulting in loss of control however the taser device is nondestructive to nerves muscles and other body elements it simply affects them in their natural mode more importantly no court of law has ever ruled that a death has ever been directly attributed to the taser device isnt high voltage lethal high voltage in itself is not dangerous one can receive a volt shock of static electricity from a doorknob on a dry day without harm the physiological effect of electrical shock is determined by the current its duration and the power source that produces the shock the typical household current of  volts is dangerous because it can pump many amperes of current throughout the body indefinitely by contrast the taser devices power supply consists of batteries that are capable of supplying electrical power for a few minutes but will not kill the assailant what are the after effects a person hit with a taser device will feel dazed for several minutes the pulsating electrical output causes involuntary muscle contractions and a resulting sense of vertigo it can momentarily stun or render an attacker unconscious yet the taser’s low electrical amperage and short duration of pulsating current ensures a nonlethal charge moreover it does not cause permanent damage or longterm aftereffects to muscles nerves or other body functions a january  annals of emergency medicine study reported taser technology leaves no long term injuries compared with  long term injuries for gunshot injuries must the probes penetrate the body to be effective no the electrical current will jump up to two inches as long as both probes are attached to clothing or skin at most only the inch needlepointhook will penetrate the skin they have less energy than a spring propelled bb what if the probe misses the taser device can be used in a touchstun mode the user is thus provided with a final backup if the probes miss the target should the user miss or engage a second attacker he can touch the unit directly to the target and it will work like a powerful touchstun device are tasers safe to use even if youve never shot a weapon taser guns are one of the best safest and most effective options for personal protection and home defense the technologically advanced taser cbolt pulse p  x series taser gun models are nonlethal weapons that are designed for both men and women to meet their self defense product needs utilizing the same technology as our proven law enforcement models they offer incredible take down power and self defense protection right in the palm of your hand check out our affordable taser sale price and buy a taser online today taser conducted electrical weapons are not considered firearms and are legal to carry in most states without permits restricted from consumer use in ma ri ny nj hi district of columbia and certain cities and counties buyer is responsible for researching and knowing the applicable state and local laws prior to purchasing possessing transporting or using a taser cew  full legal reference here       member login   email password ▶ log in dont buy any pepper spray until you read this free report  how to choose the right pepper spray gain immediate access to this report when you join our mailing list for free product tips and discounts fill in your name and email below and we’ll also send you a  coupon code you can use right away email first name    teen tracking prevention  protection your children and teenagers are subject to dangers every single day as a p