ution for managing interview room videos in the cloud policeone retrieved october     wyllie doug taser’s axon fleet brings affordable incar video solution to police policeone retrieved october     a b weise karen july   taser thinks a camera on every cop makes everyone safer bloombergcom retrieved october     smile you’re on camera the garden island retrieved april     taser unveils new wearable police cameras starting with bart venturebeat retrieved october     new holster forces all nearby body cams to start recording when gun is pulled ars technica conde nast retrieved april     electronic control device legal outline pdf   taser granted summary judgment dismissing product liability lawsuit taser international inc press release october    taser loses st productliability suit jury awards  million retrieved may     appeals court significantly reduces award in heston lawsuit against taserpermanent dead link  httpinvestortasercomphoenixzhtmlcpirolnewsarticleidhighlightpermanent dead link court grants tasers motion to reduce turner jury verdict from m to m  commons committee probes taser use by police ctvnews retrieved may     robert dziekanski taser death a homicide coroner video the huffington post retrieved may     amnesty urges moratorium on taser use after cbcradiocanada probe december   retrieved may     foxbrewster thomas december   taser employees hit itunes to troll documentary that probes suspect killings forbes retrieved december     mills chris december   taser employees appear to troll antitaser documentary with fake reviews gizmodo retrieved december     swaine jon december   taser staff appear to post negative reviews for film critical of stun guns the guardian retrieved december     is this the lawsuit that kills taser international foolcom retrieved april     taseraxon separating defense lawyers from body camera footage with license agreements  tim cushing techdirt  may  referencesedit anglen robert taser tied to independent study that backs stun gun